      <scopecontent>
         
         <head>Collection Overview</head>
         
         <p>Collection documents the artwork and printed promotional materials
		  Robert K. Jeffery commissioned, used, or referenced in diamond advertising.
		  Most items are the output of the advertising agency N. W. Ayer and Son, Inc.,
		  often featuring De Beers diamonds and outdoor advertising promotions. Other
		  items are more general to the diamond marketing industry, including marketing
		  statistics, and gemology periodicals. Acquired as part of the John W. Hartman
		  Center for Sales, Advertising &amp; Marketing History.</p>
      
      </scopecontent><!--End scopecontent--><!--Begin controlaccess--><!-- Note:  <subject>, <persname>, <corpname>, <geogname>, <famname>, <genreform>, <occupation> used where applicable -->
      
